# Common environment variables shared across all layers
# These variables are used by root compose, SAM runtime, and deployed agents.
#
# NOTE: LLM/Image service variables are managed separately in envs/llm/ profiles.
# NOTE: Broker, S3, auth, and namespace are managed per-environment in envs/overrides/.
#
# Place only variables that are truly identical across ALL environments here.
# If a variable differs between dev and prod, put it in the override files instead.

